<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُمَرُ:</span> خَطَبَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> إِلَيَّ حَفْصَةَ فَأَنْكَحْتُهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>